{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f3f2a8b962","title":"对统战部关于查询苏南破坏寺庙情况的电报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd13797eff","index":0,"year":1952,"month":12,"day":19,"articleId":"f3f2a8b962"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"003d9d7fd2","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f3f2a8b962","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长。"},{"id":"ab15657712","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f3f2a8b962","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央统战部1952年12月11日关于查询苏南破坏寺庙情况给华东局统战部的电报。电报说江苏有一些佛教徒反映：浦东“今年春天以来，拆像毁寺之风大织，几所名胜寺庵全遭破坏”；浦南的净心庵亦被摧毁无遗。电报要求华东局统战部查明真相，如情况属实应即纠正并作适当处理，并应注意其他地方有无类似情况发生。"}],"contents":[{"id":"91efd4eae4","type":"title","text":"对统战部关于查询苏南破坏寺庙情况的电报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f3f2a8b962"},{"id":"003d9d7fd2","type":"paragraph","text":"李维汉同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f3f2a8b962"},{"id":"ab15657712","type":"paragraph","text":"此件望加衔发给各中央局及各省市统战部加以注意。估计此类事各地皆有。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f3f2a8b962"},{"id":"9755cc3647","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f3f2a8b962"},{"id":"fae26b7e25","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f3f2a8b962"}],"page":{"id":"b4589ae57d","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"f3f2a8b962","start":380,"end":380}}}},"__N_SSG":true}